Third-party data attribution
----------------------------

DoppelShield ships a brand-target list (src/core/checkurl/data/
brandTargets.generated.ts) used to detect look-alike (homograph) domains. It is
derived from a public domain-popularity ranking. Only registrable domain names
are retained; the transformation is in scripts/gen-brand-targets.mjs.

The default source is the Majestic Million, published by Majestic:
  https://majestic.com/reports/majestic-million
  Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 (CC BY 3.0):
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

The generator also accepts equivalent rankings in place of Majestic Million:
  - Tranco:            https://tranco-list.eu
  - Cisco Umbrella 1M: https://umbrella.cisco.com

Each source remains under its own license and terms; this notice provides the
attribution those terms request.
